  "instructions": [
    "Heat the sesame oil in a large skillet over medium heat.",
    "Add the minced garlic and grated ginger and cook for 1 minute.",
    "Add the sliced green peppers and cook until they start to soften.",
    "In a small bowl, whisk together the gochujang, soy sauce, and brown sugar.",
    "Pour the gochujang mixture over the green peppers and stir to combine.",
    "Reduce heat to low and simmer for 10 minutes.",
    "Season with black pepper to taste.",
    "Garnish with toasted sesame seeds and chopped scallions.",
    "Serve the tang hot over rice or noodles."
  ],
